  "description": "My take on Minecraft's swords and tools, now in the style of Bare Bones!",
  "body": "<h2>Summary</h2>\n<p>I've liked playing the game with <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/bare-bones\">Bare Bones</a>, but I also enjoy the personality of my own pack, <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/skns-distinguished-tools\">SKN's Distinguished Tools</a>. So, I decided to blend them together and make a variant that fits Bare Bones. It was pretty easy, basically just recolor, make some considerations, and voila.</p>\n\n<h2>Images</h2>\n<h3>All Changes</h3>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/xCRhGIkA/images/e83adde26b0d496077afcbb5dfa0a213d0cac53c.png\">\n<h3>Weapons in Action</h3>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/xCRhGIkA/images/11a085f5dc2697fe600f5b8e66e14d88f8b45d91.png\">\n\n<hr>\n<p>If you have any questions, comments, or ideas, please check out the wiki link and post them there.</p>",
